H1.text: Where in the body is the cuboid bone. Wrist

H2.text: Where in the body is the cuboid bone. Elbow

H3.text: Where in the body is the cuboid bone. FOOT

A4.text: The five irregular bones of the midfoot, the cuboid, navicular, and three cuneiform bones, form the arches of the foot.

A5.text: The cuboid serving as its keystone, it redistributes part of the weight to the calcaneus and the distal end of the fifth metatarsal.
